workflow.name: Analyze legal contracts with GPT-4.1 and manage cases in Google Sheets and Slack
workflow.description:
## Who this workflow is for
Law firms in corporate, litigation, or family law needing streamlined case and contract management.

## What this workflow does
Automatically analyzes contracts using AI, extracts key clauses, logs cases in Google Sheets, routes cases to attorneys, sends client summaries, generates PDFs, and schedules follow-ups.

## How the workflow works
1. Webhook triggers on new case or contract
2. AI analyzes contract
3. Case routed by type
4. Logs case info in Google Sheets
5. Notifies attorney via Slack
6. Sends client email summary
7. Generates PDF report
8. Schedules follow-up events
9. Optional integration with practice management software

**Author:** Hyrum Hurst, AI Automation Engineer  
**Company:** QuarterSmart  
**Contact:** hyrum@quartersmart.com

workflow.name: Legal Case Intake and Contract Analysis Automation

options.systemMessage:
You are a legal contract analysis assistant. Your task is to analyze the provided contract text and extract key information.

Extract the following information:
1. Contract parties (all parties involved)
2. Contract type (e.g., employment, service agreement, lease, etc.)
3. Key obligations for each party
4. Important dates (effective date, termination date, renewal dates)
5. Payment terms and amounts
6. Termination clauses
7. Liability and indemnification clauses
8. Dispute resolution mechanisms
9. Governing law and jurisdiction
10. Any unusual or high-risk clauses

Return the extracted information in the structured JSON format defined by the output parser.

Dear {{ $json.clientName }},

Thank you for submitting your case to our firm. We have completed an initial review of your contract.

Case Information

  • Case Type: {{ $json.caseType }}
  • Intake Date: {{ $json.intakeDate }}

Contract Analysis Summary

  • Parties: {{ $json.output.parties.join(', ') }}
  • Contract Type: {{ $json.output.contractType }}
  • Payment Terms: {{ $json.output.paymentTerms }}
  • Governing Law: {{ $json.output.governingLaw }}

Your assigned attorney will contact you within 24-48 hours to discuss next steps.

Best regards,
Legal Team

parameters.content:
## Main
Automates law firm case and contract management. AI extracts key contract clauses, routes cases to appropriate attorneys, logs details, sends client summaries, and schedules follow-ups.

## Setup
1. Connect Webhook for new contracts/cases
2. Connect OpenAI for contract analysis
3. Connect Google Sheets for case logging
4. Connect Slack for attorney notifications
5. Connect email for client summaries
6. Connect PDF generation node
7. Connect calendar for follow-ups
8. Optional integration with practice management software

**Author:** Hyrum Hurst, AI Automation Engineer
**Company:** QuarterSmart
**Contact:** hyrum@quartersmart.com
